      "message": "swarming has decided that it won\u0027t have this 5min heuristic. I wonder if the reasoning behind that decision applies to milo as well? to me, it seems either this heuristic should be at the swarming level, or higher in the stack, perhaps at the user-level. If a user sees that a bot is dead for 1m, that\u0027s fine.\n\nregardless, this is wrong place to do the comparison with now because it is a cron job. It means that if a cron job is stuck or something, a user might see seen 1h ago and busy. If we decide that milo must have his heuristic (which I am not sure about), it should be in the presentation layer",
